<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{.Title}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; display: grid; place-items: center; }
        .card { width: min(520px, 92vw); background: #111827; border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
        button { background: #22c55e; color: #04130a; border: 0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 18px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
        code { color: #93c5fd; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Mock payment</h1>
        <p>Это тестовая страница оплаты для MVP.</p>
        <p>External payment id: <code>{{.ExternalID}}</code></p>
        <form method="post" action="/mock/payments/{{.ExternalID}}/succeed">
            <button type="submit">Подтвердить оплату</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

